            "body": "The `enable` call should go into your general config (`init.lua` or `plugin`), _not_ a ftplugin or `FileType` autocommand -- that is too late, since `enable` itself sets up such an autocommand. (You may be thinking of `lsp.start()` which is different and more low-level.)",
